<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>رَوى عنهُ جَريرُ بنُ حازمٍ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٦١٨]</span> أَبُو مُحَمدِ بنُ كَعبِ بنِ مَالكٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>رَوى عنهُ حَمّادُ بنُ سَلمةَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٦١٩]</span> أَبُو مُحمّدٍ، مَولَى قُرَيشٍ <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>عنْ عَبّادِ بنِ الرَّبيعِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>رَوى عنهُ هُشَيمٌ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
